To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private RelativeStrengthIndex _rsi;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_rsi = RSI(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_rsi.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "averageloss", _rsi.AverageLoss.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "averagegain", _rsi.AverageGain.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "relativestrengthindex", _rsi.Current.Value);
}
